snippet.title: Droogie's Screamathon 2020: C.H.A.I.N. (Haunted PS1 - Full Playthrough)
snippet.description:
Droogie's Screamathon 2020: C.H.A.I.N. (Haunted PS1 - Full Playthrough)

The Screamathon continues with a brand new set of games from Haunted PS1! In fact, all the games in this set have a cohesive narrative even though all the games were made by different developers. The logistics of accomplishing that must have been enormous. 

C.H.A.I.N. = Chronological Haunted Anomalous Interconnected Narrative
